00:01:50.967 --> 00:01:52.615
this expression right over here."

00:01:52.615 --> 00:01:54.682
When we increased d by a factor of four,

00:01:55.352 --> 00:01:58.142
the right side becomes 64 times as big,

00:01:58.142 --> 00:01:59.987
because, remember, four
to the third power.

00:02:00.737 --> 00:02:05.084
If this becomes 4d, this
becomes 64, d to the third,

00:02:05.084 --> 00:02:08.520
which we saw right over there.

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:12.050
But on the left hand side,
you have a t squared.

00:02:12.490 --> 00:02:14.418
You have a t squared.

